                       The pastebin that hopefully doesn't suck


Usage
=====

Files
-----
 Upload

  Upload a single file.
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  $ curl --upload-file vim.png https://{{ url }}/
  https://{{ url }}/xc78CK
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Upload multiple files.
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  $ curl -F a=@vim.png b=@vim2.png https://{{ url }}/
  https://{{ url }}/xc78CK
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  
